Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Difference:    Voyage generated 1:1 Point Lisas to Nantong but actual voyage stopped 2 ports in Korea before proceeding to Changzhou for final discharge.  This increased freight by $100k.  Due to the issues with Solar Ruba there seemed a chance Proman would cancel this lifting, this prevented us from being able to book the canal in time and we ended up stuck waiting the full 10 day period on our account which hurts the result.  We also slowed the ballast leg by a day as part of commercial agreement with Proman to assist them with inventory issues.  Voyage generated w/ 5% weather but actual was 14% on laden passage adding 3 days to the voyage.  This result reflects $150k hedge profit from December (Solar Ruba lift) as well as $50k hedge profit from 2022 COA hedge."},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-23T22:17:55.807","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"hire corrected to $16kpdy as per Aayush"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-14T16:32:34.497","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"updated expected wait at Changzhou...some due pilot delays at 50% laytime"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-11T22:03:43.88","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"bunkers higher on laden passage"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-02-07T15:27:21.65","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Bunker hedge of 900 mt close for Jan/Apr for lift #1 per Yvonne"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-01-27T18:51:49.78","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Panama canal waiting days increased to 10 due to covid issues"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-01-07T22:35:12.123","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"bunker stem entered at Balboa...lowering bunker average for voyage"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-01-07T17:38:24.81","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Bunker hedge for Dec close (2021 hedge profit as no 2021 Dec lifting in the system)"}],"offhireList":[{"id":189713,"dateStartUtc":"2021-12-23T23:54:00","dateEndUtc":"2021-12-31T23:59:00","days":8.09,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":"Other","remark":"Planned